{"id":286678,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-天津选举血案开庭数十人要求旁听被阻（/","date":"2013-03-29T10:16:53Z","modified":"2013-03-29T10:16:53Z","title":"维权网 | 天津选举血案开庭数十人要求旁听被阻（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span>，震惊全国的天津市北辰区辛庄因选举引发的血案，在天津市第一中级法院公开开庭审理。（以下简称天津一中院）。数十名关注此案的人士前往旁听被强行阻止，引起众人的抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>深夜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时半，原任村长黄双来带领多人连续第三夜闯入村长竞选人王复春家，打伤王复春父亲王国廷，引起村民反抗，王复春一家当时报警，但警察没有及时到达现场。在双方冲突中，黄双来等三人重伤不治身亡。此案已经是第四次开庭审理，由著名的人权律师莫少平担任被告王复春的辩护人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>来自天津、北京等地的几十名公民，手持自己的身份证依法要求参加这起震惊全国的因选举引起的血案庭审旁听，然而被天津一中院挡在门外。一个女法官直言说：“法庭太小容纳不开这么多人，只有家属能进”。引起数十名要求参加旁听的民众愤怒抗议！法庭太小不是理由，为什么不安排大法庭？大家要求见主管院长刘金波。一个法警说：“我们正在联系”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>无法进入庭审现场旁听的众人，一起在法院大门口高呼：见院长，要旁听！数十名法警、法官、保安在法院大门前阻拦。直到发稿时抗议活动仍在继续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qIUvb7rxawk/UVVW3VGdx5I/AAAAAAAAfdw/5X5AMs2AIas/s1600/1364535759759.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qIUvb7rxawk/UVVW3VGdx5I/AAAAAAAAfdw/5X5AMs2AIas/s1600/1364535759759.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dxc9ATsMqR0/UVVW4ZeuWQI/AAAAAAAAfd4/0Ri8u4r6kfE/s1600/1364535780876.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dxc9ATsMqR0/UVVW4ZeuWQI/AAAAAAAAfd4/0Ri8u4r6kfE/s1600/1364535780876.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-50Rbhg7u6F4/UVVW4lCXrkI/AAAAAAAAfeA/MsPVS7nCFcM/s1600/1364536885100.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-50Rbhg7u6F4/UVVW4lCXrkI/AAAAAAAAfeA/MsPVS7nCFcM/s1600/1364536885100.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}